display="inline"><![CDATA[g]]></fr:tex>, writing <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H\colon  f \sim  g]]></fr:tex> is given by a dependent function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[H\colon  \mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\textstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{\mathopen {}\left ({x:A}\right )\mathclose {}}}fx=gx]]></fr:tex>. We shall write <fr:tex
